data.description: RELAX POOLSIDE IN YOUR OWN BACKYARD THIS SUMMER! GREAT HOME IN WONDERFUL LAKE COMMUNITY PERFECTLY SITUATED ON 1+ ACRE LUSH PRIVATE LOT + CONNECTED TO 100 MILES OF CART PATHS! Approximately 3072 square feet + sparkling salt system pool, all surrounded by gigantic level rear yard! Entertainment size formal areas + great room, hardwood floors on 1st floor, central vacuum, intercom,  Nest smart house thermostats, security system, and oversized 2.5 car garage make this home exceptional! Stunning kitchen equipped with solid surface counters & tile backsplash! Luxurious owner's retreat + generous bedrooms (BR5 is bonus room). Neighborhood amenities offer lake, gazebo, play ground, picnic area, and fire pit! AWARD WINNING SCHOOL DISTRICT TOO! WOW!
